, and a server-side Gemini proxy ready for Cloudflare Workers.</p></div><div class=\"hero-meta\"><span class=\"pill hero-pill\">213<!-- --> spellings</span><span class=\"pill hero-pill\">200<!-- --> official sets</span><span class=\"pill hero-pill\">Gemini server-ready</span></div></section><section class=\"panel controls-panel\"><div class=\"panel-header\"><div><h2>Session</h2><p>Start smart review, trouble drill, or a SATs-style test.</p></div></div><div class=\"controls-grid\"><label class=\"field\"><span>Year group</span><select><option value=\"all\" selected=\"\">All KS2 words</option><option value=\"3-4\">Years 3-4</option><option value=\"5-6\">Years 5-6</option></select></label><label class=\"field\"><span>Round size</span><select><option value=\"8\">8 words</option><option value=\"12\" selected=\"\">12 words</option><option value=\"16\">16 words</option><option value=\"20\">20 words</option></select></label><label class=\"field\"><span>Audio engine</span><select><option value=\"gemini\" selected=\"\">Gemini TTS</option><option value=\"browser\">Browser UK TTS</option></select></label><label class=\"field\"><span>Gemini voice</span><select><option value=\"Schedar\" selected=\"\">Schedar<!-- --> (<!-- -->Even<!-- -->)</option><option value=\"Iapetus\">Iapetus<!-- --> (<!-- -->Clear<!-- -->)</option><option value=\"Kore\">Kore<!-- --> (<!-- -->Firm<!-- -->)</option><option value=\"Achird\">Achird<!-- --> (<!-- -->Friendly<!-- -->)</option><option value=\"Sulafat\">Sulafat<!-- --> (<!-- -->Warm<!-- -->)</option></select></label><label class=\"field\"><span>Playback rate</span><input type=\"range\" min=\"0.9\" max=\"1.25\" step=\"0.01\" value=\"1.05\"/><strong class=\"field-value\">1.05<!-- -->×</strong></label><label class=\"toggle-field\"><span><input type=\"checkbox\" checked=\"\"/> <!-- -->Auto-play new cards</span></label><label class=\"toggle-field\"><span><input type=\"checkbox\" checked=\"\"/> <!-- -->Show cloze sentence</span></label></div><div class=\"button-row\"><button>Smart review</button><button class=\"secondary\">Trouble drill</button><button class=\"ghost\">SATs 20 test</button></div><p class=\"status-line\">Smart review chooses due words first, then weak words, then unseen words.</p><p class=\"audio-note\">Gemini TTS ready.</p></section><section class=\"stats-grid\"><article class=\"stat-card\"><span class=\"stat-label\">Official sets</span><strong>200</strong><p>Statutory entries in this filter.</p></article><article class=\"stat-card\"><span class=\"stat-label\">Practice spellings</span><strong>213</strong><p>Expanded individual spellings.</p></article><article class=\"stat-card\"><span class=\"stat-label\">Secure</span><strong>0</strong><p>Words at two weeks or better.</p></article><article class=\"stat-card\"><span class=\"stat-label\">Due today</span><strong>0</strong><p>Already learnt, ready to revisit.</p></article><article class=\"stat-card\"><span class=\"stat-label\">New left</span><strong>213</strong><p>Not yet attempted locally.</p></article><article class=\"stat-card\"><span class=\"stat-label\">Accuracy</span><strong>—</strong><p>No scored rounds yet</p></article></section><section class=\"panel word-bank-panel\"><div class=\"panel-header\"><div><h2>Word bank</h2><p>Use the bank to start a one-word drill for any spelling.</p></div><label class=\"field bank-search\"><span>Search</span><input type=\"search\" placeholder=\"Find a spelling\" value=\"\"/></label></div><div class=\"word-groups\"><article class=\"word-group\"><h3>Years 3-4</h3><p class=\"muted-line\">0<!-- --> secure out of <!-- -->109<!-- --> visible spellings</p><div class=\"pill-wrap\"><button class=\"pill new\" title=\"accident • accident(ally) • New / due today\">accident</button><button class=\"pill new\" title=\"accidentally • accident(ally) • New / due today\">accidentally</button><button class=\"pill new\" title=\"actual • actual(ly) • New / due today\">actual</button><button class=\"pill new\" title=\"actually • actual(ly